{"tid":1246098,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"應該何時向林鄭 Say Bye-Bye","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T14:39:34.000Z","uid":266121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c40424a9ef843444eca52ee330bfc7a3817c35d0","tid":1246098,"uid":266121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"6月18日，林鄭下午4點的記者見面會，以「5個沒有」結束。晚上，繼續發信給公務員同事，指自己敏感度不足，個人要承擔責任，不過為公眾服務是其終生事業，未來會繼續帶領政府服務社會(信息源點擊鏈接)。<br />\n<br />\n上一篇文章，以國際精神科權威醫生的分析為基礎，可以非常清晰地得出結論，林鄭是一個嚴重的Hubris Syndrome(狂妄症)病患。整個「逃犯條例」的修訂，充分表現現了其好大喜功、狂妄自大的鮮明特點。最終，導致了香港及世界文明史上規模最大的遊行抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E5%90%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-say-bye-bye-29a3b3f19738?source=friends_link&amp;sk=a59cd5722e0c18d405bc5ab2ab80ccfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fmount-davis%2F%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-say-bye-bye-29a3b3f19738%3Fsource%3Dfriends_link%26sk%3Da59cd5722e0c18d405bc5ab2ab80ccfb&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranovgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=5b7e7462\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E4%BD%95%E6%99%82%E5%90%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-say-bye-bye-29a3b3f19738?source=friends_link&amp;sk=a59cd5722e0c18d405bc5ab2ab80ccfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}